Module mm
Package mm.MVC.start

Class StartView

  • java.lang.Object
    • mm.MVC.View
      • mm.MVC.start.StartView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observer
    public class StartView
extends View
    The StartView class represents the start screen of the application. It provides the main menu with options to start the game, open the level builder, and change settings. It also manages popups and overlays for level selection and the level builder UI.

    This class extends the abstract View class and implements the Observer interface to update the view according to changes in the StartModel.
